---
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro';
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  
  <Container>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-cyan-300 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Sobre Nosotros
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Somos un equipo apasionado por la tecnología y la innovación.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">
            Nuestra Historia
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Fundada con la visión de transformar negocios a través del software, Frontier Code se ha consolidado como un referente en desarrollo de soluciones tecnológicas.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Combinamos experiencia técnica con un profundo entendimiento de las necesidades empresariales para crear productos que generan valor real.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800/50 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-lg hover:border-cyan-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/50">
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">50+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-300">Proyectos</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800/50 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg hover:border-purple-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/50">
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">5+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-300">Años</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800/50 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-lg hover:border-cyan-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/50">
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">30+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-300">Clientes</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800/50 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg hover:border-purple-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/50">
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">15+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-300">Expertos</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
